{"tid":1561254,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連執紙皮婆婆都咁講","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T19:41:27.000Z","uid":296431,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e8397833b07be57d5d293a555dfe794af0fbb7c6","tid":1561254,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"文筆唔好，請見諒<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，最近就做兼職，我平時就要搬啲紙皮，俾出面既婆婆。見到佢大熱天時仲要推住成車紙皮，真係睇到都辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n  最後一日番工，就同婆婆有以下既對話（為免自爆，以下對話已修改）：<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 婆婆，我做埋後日就唔做啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 係啊？返去邊到做啊？<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 唔係啊，我之後就要繼續番學。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 哦，咁你最近有無出去抗爭啊？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：（心諗可能係伏）無啊，最近都要返工，但之前都有出去睇下既。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 係唔係因為理念關係呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： （面有難色，想解釋但又唔想自爆）⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 明白既，婆婆我都支持班年輕人，佢地係為左捍衛香港既價值。但婆婆咁既狀況，實在係去唔到幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：  理解理解，婆婆你自己都要小心，再見！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ： 好啦再見！<br />\n<br />\n  身份並唔係人最主要既價值。但當連一個拾荒婆婆都支持抗爭者，同理解佢地既做法，點解<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">位高權者</span></strong>反而<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">漠視民意</span></strong>，甚至不斷打壓社會未來既主人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 希望，香港以後既核心價值係： 民主，自由，法治。"},{"pid":"b2f1dc3d7200ad35911e369b4c3e1a290390180e","tid":1561254,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:59:55.000Z","msg":"民主，自由，法治"},{"pid":"ed93657d3622e1459f9c18e9a60eebde9ebc88f4","tid":1561254,"uid":296431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:00:20.000Z","msg":"民主，自由，法治"},{"pid":"fbab514d61fbb4c16361d36b116b3fafd03072c6","tid":1561254,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:00:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"dd0a3fda00b399fab69b16d90fe37ef5fe0f0c01","tid":1561254,"uid":56305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T14:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n紙皮婆婆通常都好正氣好sweet<br />\n<br />\n[多圖高清] [不廢up] 一人一文宣行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRzLwS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRzLwS</a>"},{"pid":"7fb3648a858c50a918b7765e146ac0599c760bb1","tid":1561254,"uid":296431,"li